OL,3,CLammy to raise MP's denial of entry to
OL,4,CHong Kong with Chinese authorities
OL,6,FThe Foreign Secretary will raise the
OL,7,Fdecision to refuse an MP entry to Hong
OL,8,FKong with Chinese authorities,
OL,9,Fdescribing the incident as "deeply
OL,10,Fconcerning".
OL,12,FLiberal Democrat MP Wera Hobhouse was
OL,13,Fdenied entry to Hong Kong on Thursday
OL,14,Fafter she had travelled to the
OL,15,Fterritory to visit her son, who has
OL,16,Flived there since 2019, and new
OL,17,Fgrandson.
