OL,3,CLammy to raise MP's denial of entry to
OL,4,CHong Kong with Chinese authorities
OL,6,FShe is believed to be the first MP to
OL,7,Fbe refused entry to the former British
OL,8,Fcolony since it was handed back to
OL,9,FChina in 1997.
OL,11,FMs Hobhouse, a member of the Inter-
OL,12,FParliamentary Alliance on China (Ipac)
OL,13,Fwhich criticises Beijing's handling of
OL,14,Fhuman rights, told The Times she had
OL,15,Fbeen given no explanation for being
OL,16,Frefused entry to Hong Kong.
