OL,3,CLammy to raise MP's denial of entry to
OL,4,CHong Kong with Chinese authorities
OL,6,FDescribing the decision as "cruel",
OL,7,Fshe added: "My son was waiting at the
OL,8,Fother end at arrivals. I couldn't even
OL,9,Fsee him and give him a hug and I
OL,10,Fhadn't seen him in a year."
OL,12,FHer parliamentary colleagues expressed
OL,13,Foutrage at the decision, with Lib Dem
OL,14,Fleader Sir Ed Davey saying it was
OL,15,F"heartless" and "totally unacceptable".
