OL,3,CLammy to raise MP's denial of entry to
OL,4,CHong Kong with Chinese authorities
OL,6,FParty foreign affairs spokesman Calum
OL,7,FMiller said the decision was "truly
OL,8,Fshocking behaviour by the Hong Kong
OL,9,Fauthorities" and called on Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary David Lammy to meet Ms
OL,11,FHobhouse "and then call the Chinese
OL,12,Fambassador for an explanation".
OL,14,FMs Hobhouse herself also called on the
OL,15,FForeign Secretary to raise the issue
OL,16,Fwith China, describing the decision as
OL,17,Fa "cruel and upsetting blow" and "an
OL,18,Finsult to all parliamentarians".
