OL,3,CLammy to raise MP's denial of entry to
OL,4,CHong Kong with Chinese authorities
OL,6,FMr Lammy said: "It is deeply
OL,7,Fconcerning to hear that an MP on a
OL,8,Fpersonal trip has been refused entry
OL,9,Fto Hong Kong.
OL,11,F"We will urgently raise this with the
OL,12,Fauthorities in Hong Kong and Beijing
OL,13,Fto demand an explanation."
OL,15,FIn addition to being a member of Ipac,
OL,16,FMs Hobhouse has previously spoken out
OL,17,Fagainst the Chinese government's abuse
OL,18,Fof human rights in Tibet and crackdown
OL,19,Fon freedom of speech in Hong Kong.
