OL,3,CLammy to raise MP's denial of entry to
OL,4,CHong Kong with Chinese authorities
OL,6,FChina has previously banned several
OL,7,FBritish MPs from entering the country,
OL,8,Fincluding Ipac members Sir Iain Duncan
OL,9,FSmith and Nusrat Ghani, and former
OL,10,Fsecurity minister Tom Tugendhat.
OL,12,FMr Lammy added: "As I made clear
OL,13,Fearlier this week, it would be
OL,14,Funacceptable for an MP to be denied
OL,15,Fentry for simply expressing their
OL,16,Fviews as a Parliamentarian.
OL,18,F"Unjustified restrictions on freedom
OL,19,Fof movement can only serve to further
OL,20,Fundermine Hong Kong's international
OL,21,Freputation."
